{
  "stem": "3659.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to torch us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're going to burn us here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they barricaded the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we tried to console everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to-- my mother was a very strong woman, and she was able to put-- instead of fear, she was able to talk to them and instill, you know, strength rather than fear into the people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very traumatic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She instilled strength in us and she says, we'll stick together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody's going to separate us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll be together, and I'll be there with you-- my sister, myself, and my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I said, she was a very strong woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally they released the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, half of the stuff was gone of their homes because they ransacked the homes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, of course, my father's business, they ransacked the whole business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the big, you know, the Star of David was in front of the building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it really-- that was on the 10th of-- 10th of November that everything just went worse and worse and worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whatever, as I said, all his inventory, even though they gave us-- it was like a pittance and barely anything, you know, of when-- what was sold in the store, but at least there was something that he was able to get.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But on the 10th of November there was nothing left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After that, it was-- the mob just walked in the-- I mean, they came in the front door, ripped all the clothing, everything, away, stripped the stores bare, and ran.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And nobody said anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, you were just-- there was a Jewish star on the front of the store, and this is-- that's a-- a Jewish business, Jude.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
